ulded containers, and souffl\u00e9/portion cups. The company's products are used in thermoforming, food and pharmaceutical packaging, box making, stationary, sweets, desserts, dry fruits, dairy, fruit and vegetables, bakery, snacks, meat/sea food, ready to eat food, beverages, nutritional products/baby, pet food, sauces/soups, confectionery, electronics, and vacuum forming applications. Rajshree Polypack Limited was founded in 1998 and is based in Thane, India."}}